Name: Multi-Quest
About the game: Multi-Quest is a very basic adventure game for new gamers that can challenge reaction time. You must travel through several worlds while dodging block enemies, clicking on objects to interact, and finding secret rooms. This game provides novice gamers a sense of accomplishment. Cats, rainbows and much more await.
